SHE CAN'T DO THATT!!!!! haha it was halarious.. 3rd goal..well i cant member how the 3rd goal was scored...

well after the game..me tay britt kel and my momma went to the grocery..idk y..cuz me and britt r leavin my moms house this week...o well.. but i didnt hav ne shoes bsides my soccer cleats..so me and taylor each put on 1 of her flippy flops,and hopped through the store..haha it was fun! : )) then we went and ate @ a chinese resturant..then dropped off tay tay..went home...and CLEANED ahhhhh!!! i had to clean my room(pretty bad..)..my closet (AHH) my drawers (even worse then my closet..) and also the playroom/gameroom...(not toooo bad) it stunk!! i cleaned for 3 hours!!! : (

my sis and my mom r @ the mall..they asked me to go..but i didn't really feel like it....

well..i'm gonna go!! byeeee!!

I had a choice of gettin my t-shirt that i hav been wanting or my cartlidge repierced and i chose my cartiladge...so my 2nd trip to FLA was so fun..just lik the first one! well tomorrow(Sunday) i hav 5v5 soccer practice at 2:00...so i will be there..well i gotta go! o ya..i missed every1 sooo much..and im sry u couldnt come ashley..but i will talk to u lata abot what we might do next year! then 1 night we went to this seafood buffet and i saw ny old boyfriend lik 5 of them ago!o ya and im at my dads house rite now so i will be bak home tomorrow night or aftanoon! 
i wish i could of saw Austin there!! 


Much <3 Taylor
